\subsubsection parameters ROS parameters

Reads and maintains the following parameters on the ROS server

- \b "~sobel_size" : \b [int] The size value of the sobel filter slope finder min: -1, default: 3, max: 7
- \b "~sobel_order" : \b [int] Value of the sobel filter order min: 1, default: 1, max: 2
- \b "~sobel_scaler" : \b [double] Value multiplied to sobel min: 1.0, default: 1.0, max: 300.0
- \b "~slope_var_thresh" : \b [double] Value for maximum change in slope min: 1.0, default: 1.0, max: 300.0

